Motech of Taiwan Expects Zero Solar-Industry Growth This Year, Times Says

-- B y   T i m   C u l p a n
-- 
2011-05-30T23:21:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-30/motech-of-taiwan-expects-zero-solar-industry-growth-this-year-times-says.html
The global solar-power industry will
face zero sales growth this year for the first time, the
Commercial Times reported today, citing  Motech Industries Inc. (6244) 
chairman Tsuo Yuan-huai. The situation will improve slightly in
the fourth quarter of this year ahead of lower subsidies in
 Germany  at the start of next year, Tsuo was cited as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tim Culpan in Taipei at 
